name: Catalan-DPO-V2
description:
Dataset Summary
	

The Catalan DPO V2 Dataset contains 23.5k sample preferences which is roughly 70% more than the Catalan DPO V1 dataset.
The dataset comprises of synthetically generated data and public preferences datasets:

argilla-orca: 9.5k preferences sampled from argilla/distilabel-intel-orca-dpo-pairs, out of which 50% were translated to Catalan
argilla-capybara: 7.2k preferences sampled from argilla/Capybara-Preferences-Filtered
